      "text": "Today, I had the opportunity to meet the fearless State and Local leaders of western North Carolina who are rebuilding their communities after the devastation of Hurricane Helene. \n\nI saw first hand hurricane damage still present and will be making sure @FEMA relief continues to help Americans rebuild their homes and communities.\n\nI am humbled and honored to serve the citizens of our great Homeland. Thanks for having me.",
